    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">Bush imagined Ramanujan and Hardy finding each other through trails&mdash;two minds describing the same problem in different vocabularies, finally linked by association rather than index. <a href="https://june.kim/pageleft-manifesto"><img src="/reading/jk.png" alt="jk" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>PageLeft Manifesto</a> imagines the same thing through embeddings: the trails are vectors now, but the problem Bush diagnosed has not changed.</p>
